title: NEW SHOW: Solvable by audiochuck
description:
A law enforcement officer and a genetic genealogist teamed up to solve one of Mississippi’s coldest cases. A Baby Doe who hadn’t had a name for decades. This past year, she finally got a name and the Solvable team is gonna take you behind the scenes to show you how… BUT what no one ever expected was that in answering the question of who Baby Doe was, it would open up an even bigger mystery...with even more victims.

Binge all 10 episodes of Solvable by audiochuck right now wherever you get your podcasts.
